      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n  - The applicant must be a bonafide resident of Odisha.\n  - The applicant must be a transgender person.\n  - The applicant must be a regular student at a recognized educational institution.\n  - The applicant’s family income should not exceed ₹2,40,000/- per annum.\n  - The applicant must not be receiving financial assistance from any other State or Central Government scheme.\n\n",
